{"comments":"HoverEffect — Interactive hover behaviors for UI elements.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nHover effects are declarative descriptions of what happens when a user\nhovers over an element. The runtime interprets these into actual\nevent handlers and animations.\n\n## Effect Categories\n\n- **Transform**: Scale, translate, rotate on hover\n- **Style**: Color, opacity, filter changes\n- **Audio**: Sound triggers on enter/leave\n- **Animation**: Lottie/CSS animation triggers\n- **Particle**: Particle burst effects\n\n## State Machine\n\n```\nidle → entering → hovering → leaving → idle\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Schema.Dimension.Temporal (timing)\n- Schema.Color.RGB (color changes)\n- Schema.Motion.Easing (transition curves)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[102,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/HoverEffect.purs","start":[102,3]},"title":"HoverIdle"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[103,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/HoverEffect.purs","start":[103,3]},"title":"HoverEntering"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[104,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/HoverEffect.purs","start":[104,3]},"title":"HoverActive"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[105,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/HoverEffect.purs","start":[105,3]},"title":"HoverLeaving"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","HoverEffect"],"HoverState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[107,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/Ho